*.pyc

# macOS
.DS_Store

# NOTE: *.rp-new files (written by update.py when it would otherwise clobber a
# locally-edited framework file) are intentionally NOT ignored, so they appear in
# `git status` as a reminder to review and merge them. Delete each after merging.

# NOTE: researchpartner.config.json is intentionally NOT ignored — a configured
# clone commits it (it is the clone's identity and update.py re-reads it).
